00:06:33.890 --> 00:06:36.700
Can you set the scene and
give us a sense of why?

00:06:36.700 --> 00:06:38.000
Why are we here today?

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:39.300
Why we have these drums?

00:06:39.300 --> 00:06:40.600
&gt;&gt; Roy Hirabayashi: Sure.

00:06:40.600 --> 00:06:45.440
Well, yes, in the late
1960's, I think probably some

00:06:45.440 --> 00:06:48.360
of you can remember at
that time was really a lot

00:06:48.360 --> 00:06:50.240
of happenings happening
in our country.

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:52.450
The Social Justice
Movement was really,

00:06:52.450 --> 00:06:54.730
the Civil Rights Movement
was really active;

00:06:54.730 --> 00:06:59.950
the Anti-War Movement was going
on, and so at that time it was also

00:06:59.950 --> 00:07:02.670
