00:11:28.690 --> 00:11:30.820
This is the way I'm going
to communicate with you.

00:11:30.820 --> 00:11:34.870 position:56%
This is how loud I'm going to become
that I could not show you as I

00:11:34.870 --> 00:11:37.270
as growing up as a little girl.

