00:32:28.570 --> 00:32:30.530
So, if you can be patient

00:32:30.530 --> 00:32:33.940
and understand that's what
we're exploring, then yeah,

00:32:33.940 --> 00:32:39.080
come join San Jose Taiko and to
be respectful of the tradition

00:32:39.080 --> 00:32:43.520
and the history of like what
this community has gone through.

00:32:43.520 --> 00:32:48.310
&gt;&gt; Daniel Sheehy: San Jose
