00:47:37.520 --> 00:47:39.160
There are all kinds
of ways to innovate.

00:47:39.160 --> 00:47:41.670
This is another way to innovate.

00:47:41.670 --> 00:47:42.970
&gt;&gt; Roy Hirabayashi: Right.

