And so, we just feel we're trying
to put it under one category roof

00:47:56.140 --> 00:48:00.250
of terminology in a sense, but
really it's our outreach program,

00:48:00.250 --> 00:48:05.830
our master classes that we offer
for college to other adults.

00:48:05.830 --> 00:48:09.040
So, it's a variety of classes,
and our training program we have

00:48:09.040 --> 00:48:10.900
for our performing members.

00:48:10.900 --> 00:48:13.650
We feel we have probably one of
the most vigorous training programs

00:48:13.650 --> 00:48:15.600
for a member to join San Jose Taiko

00:48:15.600 --> 00:48:17.970
that exists here in
the US right now.

00:48:17.970 --> 00:48:20.970
And so, all of these things
are part of what we consider

00:48:20.970 --> 00:48:24.970
as an important part of teaching
Taiko and also spreading it

00:48:24.970 --> 00:48:28.510
to our performances, whether it's
our concert programming o outreach

00:48:28.510 --> 00:48:31.990
program into the schools,
our festival programming,

00:48:31.990 --> 00:48:36.060
and our touring that we
do as an ensemble; and so,

00:48:36.060 --> 00:48:38.680
it's something that's
been going on for a while.

00:48:38.680 --> 00:48:41.660
We're now on the verge of,
actually, an important piece

00:48:41.660 --> 00:48:45.630 position:56%
for us has been a physical site, and
