00:48:54.120 --> 00:48:57.110
so if anyone wants to support it.

00:48:57.110 --> 00:48:59.100
I know you probably
understand what that means.

00:48:59.100 --> 00:49:01.700
&gt;&gt; PJ Hirabayashi: And it's
happening in San Jose Japantown.

00:49:01.700 --> 00:49:04.210
&gt;&gt; Roy Hirabayashi: It's in San
Jose Japantown, so we're very proud

00:49:04.210 --> 00:49:05.900
of that too, and we're partnering

00:49:05.900 --> 00:49:07.460
with several other
arts organizations,

00:49:07.460 --> 00:49:09.870
