00:50:52.900 --> 00:50:54.200
&gt;&gt; Yes.

00:50:54.200 --> 00:50:55.500
&gt;&gt; Daniel Sheehy: Yeah, okay.

00:50:55.500 --> 00:50:56.800
So, let's have another question.

00:50:56.800 --> 00:50:58.100
&gt;&gt; That's okay.

00:50:58.100 --> 00:50:59.400
Just --

00:50:59.400 --> 00:51:02.690
&gt;&gt; I'm just wondering, you
know, I'm from Indonesia,

00:51:02.690 --> 00:51:09.560
and we sort of regard our
instruments as, I don't know,

00:51:09.560 --> 00:51:15.690
holy or sacred, or we
have to respect them.

00:51:15.690 --> 00:51:20.480
Do you teach them to respect
like you cannot step over it,

00:51:20.480 --> 00:51:23.450
and you don't put stuff on it?

00:51:23.450 --> 00:51:26.190
And people don't understand,
you know,

00:51:26.190 --> 00:51:30.910
and so you always have
to teach them.

00:51:30.910 --> 00:51:32.210
&gt;&gt; PJ Hirabayashi: Yes.

00:51:32.210 --> 00:51:38.560
There's the values that are
integrated towards the practicing

00:51:38.560 --> 00:51:42.810
of Taiko, and just because
Taiko itself is made

00:51:42.810 --> 00:51:51.260
out of three natural elements,
wood from tree, hide from animal,

00:51:51.260 --> 00:51:56.990
metal tacks from earth, you know,
just to really understand, wow,

00:51:56.990 --> 00:52:00.110
this is what's gifting
us with this sound,

00:52:00.110 --> 00:52:03.790
and each sound has its own voice.

00:52:03.790 --> 00:52:06.930
How do you respect even that voice?

00:52:06.930 --> 00:52:09.710
Like this drum is like
another person.

00:52:09.710 --> 00:52:15.040
How do you respect that drum
as I can equally respect you?

00:52:15.040 --> 00:52:19.350
So, it's like looking at
each as a living being.

00:52:19.350 --> 00:52:20.650
&gt;&gt; Roy Hirabayashi: Yeah

00:52:20.650 --> 00:52:22.600
&gt;&gt; I think, you know,
lots of people don't,

00:52:22.600 --> 00:52:26.450
I think lots of people don't
understand that, you know.

00:52:26.450 --> 00:52:29.890
&gt;&gt; PJ Hirabayashi: Thank
you for asking that.

00:52:29.890 --> 00:52:31.190
&gt;&gt; Roy Hirabayashi: Yes.

00:52:31.190 --> 00:52:33.210
